          "reviewBody": "People should stop giving importance to such institutes which are implementing faulty selection process. \nLots based system is beeinc followed just to portray that they are fair. But in reality they are lazy to evaluate the child`s background, family, parents education and profession. Behind the curtains they are giving admissions to ultra rich students on hidden management seats. Not prioritising the students who lives nearby. No sports Infra, Modern teaching facilities\n\nWhen you visit for enquiry they just tell that admissions will be done on lots. \nNo school walk- through, no proper orientation is provided. \n\nRude admin staff just says if you have ultra high leve of contacts then you may get the management seat else just rely on lottery. There are much better schools in the city. People should stop giving unnecessary importance to such arrogantly administrated institute.",
